'''Council Rock''' was a sheer black mesa on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]], ringed with observation platforms, where the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Rock Council|government]] met.

Before the [[Battle of Kashyyyk (Second Galactic Civil War)|Battle of Kashyyyk]], [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] reunited with [[Tarfang]] and [[Jae Juun]], who attempted to arrest the Solos. Leia and Tarfang fought over the [[Tyrossum]] jawbone for control of the conversation as per customs. Since Leia was not able to use the Force the battle was difficult and brutal with Tarfang trying to choke Leia and bash her head against the rock. Eventually Leia tossed Tarfang off of the rock just as Luke arrived. Tarfang gave the jawbone, which granted whoever held it the right to speak at the Council, to Luke.

